And I've got your motion
sickness pills and your Lysol.

01:34.261 --> 01:36.355
What have you got
in these bags, anyway?

01:36.463 --> 01:38.363
Just light summer wear.

01:38.465 --> 01:40.559
For how many summers, Marion?

